{
  "stem": "24830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I send him to Switzerland, because the problem, he was 16-- 15, I think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was 15.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was-- he was too old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was to wear, you know, short pants.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he finally went through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister was in the United State.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Did you-- were you aware of what was going on in-- in other places?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you have--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the news-- yeah, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we listen to the, you know, Radio London and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I live alone most of the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there is much more to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I want to-- I want to tell you, like, my state of mind, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I was still young, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wanted to look good anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember I had-- I order some shoes, these platform-- covered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted it covered with certain color.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they told you-- they told me it will take two weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to myself, oh, I hope I will wear them before I get caught.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- I wanted to wear these shoes before I get caught.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see what my state of mind?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's when-- and then another time, once in a while, you know, to forget, I went to see a movie.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the movie, you feel when-- when it's the end of the movie.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can feel it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I felt the end of the movie, I started to be oppress-- you know, like, I say, oh my God.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I still have to go out and live, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How long will I-- how long will I, you know, will I survive?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that was the feeling I have.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I didn't want the end of the movie.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
